thread.title: Gordon Holusa

author: Gordon Holusa
title: Gordon Holusa
text:
After trying a variety of different ways to send funds i found Torfx after reading favourable reviews online
From her first contact to finalizing my first transfer Rachael was pleasant patient and very professional
In this online world that people have to deal with Torfx is on a real winner by providing one on one personal contact
Rachael's manner is exemplary
